title: Chicago Skyline Wood Wrapped Candle
description:
The candle's Chicago skyline design is created using a wrapped Mahogany wood cutout.  The square glass soy-based candle stays lit for about 30 hours and is a great gift for any candle lover or addition to your living room, bathroom or bedroom. Designed and crafted in Chicago by a former student of The Art Institute.

6 in. x 6 in. x 6 in
